      <title>韩国法院在选举案中与反对派领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/south-korea-court-sides-with-opposition-leader-in-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国法院裁定，该国的主要反对派领导人李·蒙蒙（Lee Jae-Myung）没有违反选举法，推翻了下级法院的裁决，并加强了他作为潜在总统领先者的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/south-korea-court-sides-with-opposition-leader-in-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 06:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安（Erdogan</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/erdogan-gets-trump-praise-amid-crackdown-that-s-rattled-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）赞扬土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan），向政府承认，在对反对派的镇压下，在国内面临一周的抗议活动和外国资本的逃亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/erdogan-gets-trump-praise-amid-crackdown-that-s-rattled-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 06:20:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列作为新国防学说的一部分在叙利亚部署部队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/israel-deploys-troops-in-syria-as-part-of-new-defense-doctrine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蓝色的联合国维持和平人员大部分都消失了，由成千上万的以色列部队在九个新基地中，一直到大马士革。一个六米深的（20英尺）的沟渠正在从火山岩中挖出，以将任何向以色列滚动的东西捕获。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/israel-deploys-troops-in-syria-as-part-of-new-defense-doctrine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 06:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
