      <title>梅尔斯的下一个大考试是赢得德国保守主义者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/merz-s-next-big-test-is-to-win-over-german-conservative-skeptics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）面临着一个关键的时刻，他成为德国总理，因为心怀不满的保守派担心自己做了太多让步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/merz-s-next-big-test-is-to-win-over-german-conservative-skeptics</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
