    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡总理认为到2028年的经济脆弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/sri-lanka-s-prime-minister-sees-fragile-economy-through-2028</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理说，斯里兰卡的新政府将在至少在接下来的两年内支出的数量受到限制，因为它希望平衡竞选活动的承诺，以减轻税收的增加和其他紧缩措施，并限制其30亿美元的救助计划所设定的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/sri-lanka-s-prime-minister-sees-fragile-economy-through-2028</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 04:35:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大和印度希望与特朗普的职责相抵触</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/canada-india-look-to-deescalate-tensions-to-counter-trump-s-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大和印度正在采取措施降低外交紧张局势的升级，包括苛刻的指控和谴责，因为双方都旨在加强贸易关系以应对美国关税威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/canada-india-look-to-deescalate-tensions-to-counter-trump-s-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 04:32:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国有影响力的人从台湾被驱逐出来以支持入侵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/china-influencer-forced-to-leave-taiwan-for-supporting-invasion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名中国有影响力的人因支持军事夺取自我运营的民主的军事驱逐而被驱逐出境，已返回她的国家。随着台北加紧努力来反击北京的宣传。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/china-influencer-forced-to-leave-taiwan-for-supporting-invasion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 01:57:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普可能会在数周内实施铜进口关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，美国对铜进口的关税可能会在几周内，比判决的截止日期提前几个月。在纽约交易的铜升至纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 01:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安仔细踩踏以平息抗议和平静的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/erdogan-treads-carefully-to-quell-protests-and-calm-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷切普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）正在采取措施，以确保全国各地的抗议活动不会恶化并在金融市场中遏制溃败，即使他把螺丝钉戴上对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/erdogan-treads-carefully-to-quell-protests-and-calm-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 17:10:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
